vedate = 2020-09-12 }}</ref>、[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的[[切尔诺贝利|切尔诺贝利]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://edition.cnn.com/travel/article/dark-tourism-chernobyl/index.html |title = Chernobyl and the dangerous ground of 'dark tourism' |last = Chance |first = Matthew |last2 = Ullah |first2 = Zahra |date = 2019-06-25 |publisher = CNN Travel |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721125221/https://edition.cnn.com/travel/article/dark-tourism-chernobyl/index.html |archivedate = 2020-07-21 }}</ref>以及美國[[九一一襲擊事件|九一一襲擊事件]]的[[原爆點|原爆點]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.theage.com.au/world/tragedy-turns-to-tourism-at-ground-zero-20020629-gducga.html |title = Tragedy turns to tourism at Ground Zero |author = New York Times |date = 2002-06-29 |publisher = The Age |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200912063647/https://www.theage.com.au/world/tragedy-turns-to-tourism-at-ground-zero-20020629-gducga.html |archivedate = 2020-09-12 }}</ref>）。另外，相關的景點還包括曾發生人類暴行和種族滅絕的地點（[[波蘭|波蘭]]的[[奧斯威辛集中營|奧斯威辛集中營]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/lavanyasunkara/2019/08/01/from-auschwitz-to-chernobyl-tips-on-respectfully-visiting-dark-tourism-sites/#7c7d3efd20e6 |title = From Auschwitz To Chernobyl: Tips On Respectfully Visiting Dark Tourism Sites |last = Sunkara |first = Lavanya |date = 2019-08-01 |publisher = Forbes |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200129170946/https://www.forbes.com/sites/lavanyasunkara/2019/08/01/from-auschwitz-to-chernobyl-tips-on-respectfully-visiting-dark-tourism-sites/#7c7d3efd20e6 |archivedate = 2020-01-29 }}</ref>、[[中國|中國]]的[[侵華日軍南京大屠殺遇難同胞紀念館|南京大屠殺紀念館]]<ref name="HK01@180130">{{Cite web |url = https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E5%87%BA%E8%B5%B0/154937/%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%97%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A-%E4%BE%86%E7%A8%BF-%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E7%81%BD%E9%9B%A3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E4