== 批評 ==
儘管在黑暗觀光中遊客能了解相關歷史，但這亦衍生了不少的道德問題。有些旅行社為了吸引更多遊客及增加收入，而歪曲甚至捏造事實，或者增加血腥因素以產生戲劇性效果<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.nationalgeographic.com/travel/features/is-dark-tourism-ok-chernobyl-pripyat-disaster-sites/ |title = Is 'Dark Tourism' OK? |last = Reid |first = Robert |date = 2016-04-26 |publisher = National Geographic |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-12 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200726162954/https://www.nationalgeographic.com/travel/features/is-dark-tourism-ok-chernobyl-pripyat-disaster-sites/ |archivedate = 2020-07-26 }}</ref>。另外，有意見認為黑暗觀光是「消費死者」，甚至是「消費受難者的傷痛」<ref name="HK01@180130"/>{{sfn|Elkington|Gammon|2013|pp=54-55}}。

